<subSubSection id="B4F06548B11CA13CEBFDFB3BE568FA32" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FC5536C3B11CA13CEBFDFB3BE568FA32" blockId="16.[151,1436,1186,1463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">
<emphasis id="CE9EEAD1B11CA13CEBFDFB3BE151FA86" bold="true" box="[199,315,1258,1283]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">Remarks.</emphasis>
This distinctive species was originally described by 
<bibRefCitation id="987B4B32B11CA13CE8A3FB3BE40AFA86" author="Loveridge" box="[921,1120,1258,1283]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" refString="Loveridge, A. (1944) New geckos of the genera Afroedura, new genus, and Pachydactylus from Angola. American Museum Novitates, 1254, 1 - 4." type="journal article" year="1944">
Loveridge (
<number id="4A2224E4B11CA13CEF24FB3AE432FA86" box="[1054,1112,1259,1283]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" value="1944.0">1944</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
as 
<taxonomicName id="3BEA4D40B11CA13CEFB3FB3AE50EFA86" box="[1161,1380,1258,1283]" class="Reptilia" family="Gekkonidae" genus="Afroedura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="karroica" subSpecies="bogerti">
<emphasis id="CE9EEAD1B11CA13CEFB3FB3AE50EFA86" box="[1161,1380,1258,1283]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">A. karroica bogerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and was only elevated to specific status by 
<bibRefCitation id="987B4B32B11CA13CE971FADFE37EFAA2" author="Onderstall" box="[587,788,1294,1319]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" refString="Onderstall, D. (1984) Descriptions of two new subspecies of Afroedura pondolia (Hewitt) and a discussion of species groups within the genus (Reptilia: Gekkonidae). Annals of the Transvaal Museum, 33, 497 - 509." type="journal article" year="1984">
Onderstall (
<number id="4A2224E4B11CA13CE9F5FADEE366FAA2" box="[719,780,1295,1319]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" value="1984.0">1984</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<taxonomicName id="3BEA4D40B11CA13CE825FADFE383FAA2" box="[799,1001,1294,1319]" class="Reptilia" family="Gekkonidae" genus="Afroedura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bogerti">
<emphasis id="CE9EEAD1B11CA13CE825FADFE383FAA2" box="[799,1001,1294,1319]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">Afroedura bogerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="3BEA4D40B11CA13CEF25FADEE4F7FAA2" box="[1055,1181,1294,1319]" class="Reptilia" family="Gekkonidae" genus="Afroedura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Squamata" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="karroica">
<emphasis id="CE9EEAD1B11CA13CEF25FADEE4F7FAA2" box="[1055,1181,1294,1319]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">A. karroica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
possess the diagnostic features of different species groups and are separated from one another by a disjunction of approximately 
<quantity id="3B129B26B11CA13CEE08FAE2E5FDFACE" box="[1330,1431,1330,1355]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" unit="km" value="2000.0">2000 km</quantity>
; that they were previously considered conspecific is illustrative of the fact that herpetologists were reluctant to erect new specific level taxa for geckos of this genus, presumably because of the their general morphological conservatism (
<bibRefCitation id="987B4B32B11CA13CEA03FA4FE189FA32" author="Jacobsen" box="[313,483,1438,1463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" refString="Jacobsen, N. H. G. (1997) Family Gekkonidae, Genus Afroedura. In: Van Wyk, J. H. (Ed.), Proceedings of the FitzSimons Commemorative Symposium, South African Lizards: 50 years of Progress and Third H. A. A. Symposium on African Herpetology, Transvaal Museum, Pretoria, South Africa, 11 - 15 October 1993. Herpetological Association of Africa, Stellenbosch, pp. 34 - 39." type="journal article" year="1997">
Jacobsen 
<number id="4A2224E4B11CA13CEA9DFA4EE189FA32" box="[423,483,1439,1463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" value="1997.0">1997</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="987B4B32B11CA13CEACCFA4EE291FA32" author="Barts" box="[502,763,1438,1463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" refString="Barts, M. &amp; Haacke, W. D. (2010) Afroedura bogerti Loveridge, 1944. Bogert's Flat Gecko. Reproduction. African Herp News, 50, 39." type="journal article" year="2010">
Barts &amp; Haacke (
<number id="4A2224E4B11CA13CE982FA4EE299FA32" box="[696,755,1439,1463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="467" value="2010.0">2010</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
provided data about reproduction in captivity.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
